nodes.description: Lost his job as a banker and is starting a dance studio. | Looking for the ideal spot for his dance studio and considering Marley flooring for the dance floor. | Started hitting the gym last week to stay on track with the venture. | Thanks for being there for me. Your help means a lot. | Thanks for being there for me. Your words motivate me to keep going! | I'm gonna keep on believing in myself. Thanks for the kind words! | Shut down bank account to help biz grow | Turning his loves of dance into a business. Students are excelling. Learning with them. | Attended a fair to showcase his dance studio, received some leads, and learned about the challenges of running a business. | Hi! Since we last spoke I am still working on the dance studio and things are looking up! | It's a bit scary, but I just think about my love for dance and how it makes me feel. It's been my stress-buster since childhood! | Yeah, Gina! Dancing helps me de-stress. It's where I'm most alive. It's a must-have in my life. | Dancing is like second nature to me. I'm living my dream by having my own dance studio and teaching others. | Thanks! Your help means a lot. Keep you posted on the dance studio progress. | Wow, Gina, I'm stoked about this! Taking a risk is scary, but I'm sure following my dreams will pay off in the end. How did the interview go? | Glad to hear it. Been practicing dance routines lately, it keeps my mind focused and motivated. | Sure, Gina! Wanna see one of my routines? Lemme know when you got time and I'll send you a vid. | Thanks a lot! Your help really means a lot. I'll get the video to you soon! | Prepping for his dance studio more than ever. | Got mentored by a business guy yesterday. | Taking a short trip to Rome to clear his mind | Attending networking events to promote his business | Writing all plans down to track progress | Learning marketing and analytics tools to push the biz forward | Rehearsing hard and working on business plans. Dancing has kept him going.

Lost her job at Door Dash and is passionate about contemporary dance. | Launched an ad campaign for her clothing store and is excited about its success. | I'm here for you, rooting for you all the way. | Believe in yourself. Even when it's tough, you got this! Keep going! | Supporting Jon's dance studio | Trophies from dance contests as a reminder of hard work and joy. | Hi! You're so inspiring taking it on and opening your own studio! | Gotcha, Jon! Dance is my stress fix too. As soon as I start, all my worries vanish. It's amazing what we can do for our own mental health with something we enjoy. | I get it, Jon. Dance is just me -- I can't picture life without it. It's like air. | You're living the dream and inspiring others too! Your studio will totally change things for lots of folks. | Thanks! Really appreciate you keeping me in the loop on this cool project. Can't wait to hear more and watch it come to life! | Oh, btw, I had an interview for a design internship yesterday! It was so cool. | It was great! | Wow! That's great. Dancing is awesome for staying focused. Wanna show me a routine sometime? | Yeah, Jon, I'll watch your routine! So proud of you! | No prob! Always here to help. Can't wait to see the vid! | Got accepted for a fashion internship | Supporting Jon and being proud of his achievements | Acquired new unique pieces for her store | Built a new website for customers to make orders
Created by relation | Grand opening is happening tomorrow | Savoring the good vibes and capturing the joy and thrill of dance | Making memories and having fun
